messages.messageBody:
Something else she might want to consider at some point would be hospital
social worker. I think it's part of their job to help families through
tough decisions and experiences at the hospital.
This is my field. It's a great job with some flexibility to allow me to homeschool and be home more with kids + it's high drama and so am I. Kelli
